# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# canton-vc verifier-demo — environment configuration
#
# Default mode is `mock` — the demo runs entirely in the browser
# against a deterministic in-browser provider plus an in-memory
# Canton mock. No env needed; just `pnpm dev`.
#
# For real KYC vendor sandbox testing, paste your sandbox keys below
# and pick the matching vendor from the SPA header dropdown.
#
# IMPORTANT: server-side names (no VITE_ prefix). Vite loads these
# into the Node process for the vendor-proxy plugin to read —
# they NEVER reach the browser bundle, so HMAC secrets / API keys
# stay private. Free sandbox tiers:
#
#   Didit:    https://didit.me     (sign up, free tier)
#   Sumsub:   https://sumsub.com   (sign up, free tier — sbx: prefix)
#   Persona:  https://withpersona.com  (sign up, free tier)
# --------------------------------------------------------------------

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Didit
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# DIDIT_API_KEY=
# DIDIT_KYC_WORKFLOW_ID=
# DIDIT_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
# DIDIT_BASE_URL=https://verification.didit.me

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Sumsub
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# SUMSUB_APP_TOKEN=
# SUMSUB_SECRET_KEY=
# SUMSUB_LEVEL_NAME_IDENTITY=basic-kyc-level
# SUMSUB_WEBHOOK_SECRET=
# SUMSUB_BASE_URL=https://api.sumsub.com

# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# Persona
# --------------------------------------------------------------------
# PERSONA_API_KEY=
# PERSONA_TEMPLATE_ID=
# PERSONA_WEBHOOK_SECRETS=
# PERSONA_BASE_URL=https://withpersona.com/api/v1
